title: Maps of Iceland (1:50k/100k/250k/500k/750k) [GeoTIFF, PNG, JPG]
description:
This mapping package contains maps of Iceland in formats intended for
the widest possible use, as opposed hitherto realesed proprietary
mapping packages which have been meant to restrict their use and
distribution.

= Maps included

== 1:50.000 UTM maps

102 maps covering part of Iceland (see
generated/1-050k/1-050k-index.png for coverage). Surveyed around 1955
these maps use the Universal Transverse Mercator (UTM) coordinate system.

Included in GeoTIFF and PNG versions, both of which have
georeferencing metadata.

== 1:100.000 "Atlaskort" maps

87 maps covering the whole of Iceland (see
generated/1-100k/1-100k-index.png for coverage). Surveyed from
1900-193.

== 1:250.000 maps

1:250.000 maps based on the 1:100.000 maps covering the whole of
Iceland in 9 map sheets

Included in GeoTIFF and PNG versions, both of which have
georeferencing metadata.

== 1:500.000 map

A single 1:500.000 map sheet covering the whole of Iceland.

Included in GeoTIFF and PNG versions, both of which have
georeferencing metadata.
